The Annex to Regulation (EU) No 7/2010 is hereby amended as follows:
(1) the rows for the tariff quotas with order numbers 09.2767, 09.2813 and 09.2631 are replaced by the rows set out in Annex I to this Regulation;
(2) the rows for the tariff quotas with order numbers 09.2977, 09.2628, 09.2629 and 09.2635 are replaced by the rows set out in Annex II to this Regulation;
(3) the row for the tariff quota with order number 09.2947 is deleted.
